Cheryl Cole Officially Confirms Pregnancy, Expecting First Baby With Liam Payne posted by Holly Nicol - share 
Cheryl Cole officially confirmed she’s expecting a baby with Liam Payne in an Instagram post on Thursday. 
After months of speculation, the British star finally confirmed her pregnancy in a shoot for a new ad campaign for The Prince’s Trust and L’Oreal Paris. Alongside a picture from the shoot, in which the pop star can be seen holding her hands underneath her stomach, Cole wrote, “I am proud to announce that I am one of fifteen ambassadors working with @PrincesTrust & LOreal Paris UK to help thousands of young people turn self-doubt into self-worth. The “All Worth It” Confidence training program starts now! #ALLWORTHIT #PRINCESTRUSTLOREAL.” 
